      => 'TextureLayer @03e9bf99-adf2-45d0-bc58-9354758e2748 
      {
        label = "BPMSystem + Energy + Speed", 
        generator = => 'Compo @03e9bf99-4acd-45d0-bc58-2dd442ed2ea1 
        {
          tools = 
          {
            => 'DescriptionTool @03e9bf99-f9b7-45d0-bc58-1799ebab94c7 
            {
              author = "Paul-Ernest Martin", 
              documentation = "BPM System Enables to extract BPM. With that set a linear loop lentgh to have a parameter \"BPMx5\" that goes from zero to 100% with frequency 5 times sower that the BPM of the current music.
Connect in Shared Banks : 
- Main Timeline Speed to the speed of the video
- Percentage for current Energy for all system that requires to have the current energy of the song
- Trigger : detect Changement energy detector 
- Bpm x 5 -> Restart from begin useful with BPM Manual Detector.
IN Links:  
- Bass Filter uinput to detect BPM.
- Linear Loop Length -> extract from BPM Detector to have clean 0 to 100% in fonction of BPM.
- Mean Extractor better input for Energy Extractor.
- BPM to VideoSpeed to have the speed ideal for the video.
- Control UI Display -> is for having all the important \"read\" values or \"write\" values"
